 Because they're your friend you can trust that they will treat you fair and do a good job vs a stranger. But it doesn't mean it should be a free job. Something simple sometimes a few beers are enough but always offer a fair rate if you don't want them to start avoiding you. Also don't only call them when you need something, that's not a real friendship.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/DOhiKDv</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[researchonyourown]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>My great great uncle's sword from the First World War</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/Wv8ynX3</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/0BN9pab.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/wC0xrnT.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/QyPYU3Z.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Rpv8pux.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/h11zRmG.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/Wv8ynX3</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Birdbrickman95]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Girls will be Girls</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/H9gWgfp</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/bSCbuJm.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/H9gWgfp</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Lefty212]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>She wants the new one</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/JuMdo4U</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/6e985Ld.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/JuMdo4U<